    API for the Auton class Usage : Adding an auton: Toggling Autons: 1) call "toggleAuton" 2) It will automatically go through all the autons and show them on the DS Calling Auton: 1) on autonomousInit, call auton.initialize() 2) during autonomousPeriodic, call auton.execute() TODO :
